# {{zh-div|水|河}} {{w|zh:汝水|Ru River}}, a [[northern]] [[tributary]] of the [[Huai River]] in modern-day [[southern]] [[Henan]] [[province]]. The name also refers to the {{w|Hong River (Huai River Tributary)|Hong River}} in its lower reaches, which now shares a common course with the Ru, as well as a southern tributary of the Hong.
# {{lb|zh|literary|or|coastal|_|Min}} [[thou]], [[you]] {{gloss|second-person pronoun}}
#* {{zh-x|^子-貢 問 曰：「^賜 也 何如？」^子.曰：「'''女{rǔ}''' 器 也。」|Zigong asked, "What do you say of Ci [Zigong's given name]?" The Master said, "'''You''' are a utensil."|ref=Analects}}
# {{surname|lang=zh}}

{{ja-readings
|goon=にょ
|kanon=じょ
|kun=い-, まし-, いまし-, みまし-, うぬ, し, な-, なれ-, なむち-, なむじ-<なむぢ-, なんじ-<なんぢ-
}}

{{ja-kanjitab|yomi=k|まし}}

The [[nominalization]] of [[honorific]] verb {{m|ja|坐す|tr=masu||to be|pos=honorific}}.<ref name="KDJ">{{R:Kokugo Dai Jiten}}</ref>

Alternatively, a shortening of ''imashi''<ref name="KDJ">{{R:Kokugo Dai Jiten}}</ref><ref name="DJR">{{R:Daijirin}}</ref> (see below).

{{ja-pos|pronoun|まし}}

# {{lb|ja|sort=まし|obsolete|informal}} {{n-g|second person pronoun}}: [[you]]
#* {{RQ:Man'yōshū|14|3440}}
#*: 許乃河泊尓 安佐菜安良布児 奈礼毛安礼毛 余知乎曽母弖流 伊仾児多婆里尓 <sub>一云 '''麻之'''毛安礼母</sub>

{{ja-kanjitab|yomi=k|いまし}}

The [[nominalization]] of [[honorific]] verb {{m|ja|坐す|tr=imasu||to be|pos=honorific}}.<ref name="KDJ">{{R:Kokugo Dai Jiten}}</ref>

Possibly also analyzable as a compound of {{prefix|ja|sort=いまし|汝|tr1=i|t1=you|坐|tr2=mashi|t2=presence; being|pos2=the {{m|ja|連用形|tr=ren'yōkei||continuative or stem form}} of honorific verb {{m|ja|坐す}} ''masu'', “to be”}}.

{{ja-pos|pronoun|いまし}}

# {{lb|ja|sort=いまし|obsolete|polite}} {{n-g|second person pronoun}}: [[you]]
#* {{RQ:Man'yōshū|11|2517}}
#*: 足千根乃 母尓障良婆 無用 '''伊麻思'''毛吾毛 事應成
#* {{RQ:Man'yōshū|14|3359}}
#*: 駿河能宇美 於思敝尓於布流 波麻都豆良 '''伊麻思'''乎多能美 波播尓多我比奴 <sub>一云 於夜尓多我比奴</sub>
#* 797: [[w:Shoku Nihongi|Shoku Nihongi]] (edict #29)
#*: 朕子'''伊末之'''<small>仁</small>授給

{{ja-kanjitab|yomi=k|な}}

From {{inh|ja|ojp|sort=な|-}}, from {{inh|ja|jpx-pro|sort=な|*na}}. Possibly cognate with {{cog|ko|너||you|pos=second-person singular informal pronoun}}.

Also found in some instances as a self-reference, {{m|en|one}}, {{m|en|oneself}}. This sense is more commonly spelled {{m|ja|己}} when used in isolation.<ref name="KDJ">{{R:Kokugo Dai Jiten}}</ref> Possibly cognate with {{cog|ko|나||I|pos=first-person singular informal pronoun}}.

{{ja-pos|pronoun|なれ}}

# {{lb|ja|sort=な|obsolete}} {{n-g|second person pronoun}}: [[you]]
#* {{RQ:Man'yōshū|14|3440}}
#*: 許乃河泊尓 安佐菜安良布児 '''奈礼'''毛安礼毛 余知乎曽母弖流 伊仾児多婆里尓 <sub>一云 麻之毛安礼母</sub>
#* c. 913 [[w:Kokin Wakashū|Kokin Wakashū]] (#904)
#*: ちはやぶる宇治のはしもり '''なれ'''をしぞあはれとは思ふ 年のへぬれば

{{ja-kanjitab|yomi=k|なむぢ}}

{{IPAchar|/namuti/}} → {{IPAchar|/namudi/}} → {{IPAchar|/namud͡ʑi/}}

From earlier {{m|ja|なむち|tr=namuchi}}. Final voicing due to influence of medial voiced {{IPAchar|/m/}}.

{{ja-pos|pronoun|なむじ|hhira=なむぢ}}

# {{lb|ja|sort=なむぢ|obsolete}} {{n-g|second person pronoun}}: [[you]]
#* {{RQ:Taketori Monogatari}}
#*: 大納言わらゐて、「'''なむぢ'''らが君の使と名を流しつ。君の仰ごとをば、いかが背くべき」との給て [...]
#* {{RQ:Taketori Monogatari}}
#*: 大納言起きゐてのたまはく、「'''汝（なむぢ）'''らよくもて來ずなりぬ。龍は鳴る神のるいにこそありけれ。[...]」

{{ja-pos|pronoun|なんじ|hhira=なんぢ}}

